			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1) Goto 12.1, -51.6, -51 or bookmark &quot;BGO_Rivington_AngleIronSmithy&quot;.&#xD;&#xA;2) Encounter with Orin who's disguised as the smith.&#xD;&#xA;3) After the encounter, the real Smith will appear and talk to the players." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="330" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Gyldro Angleiron the Smith unknowingstly was knocked unconcious by Orin the Red.  He only awakes once Orin the Red has teleported away - leaving the players with the awkward circumstance of being at his smithy.  He views the players with suspicion until convinced either-wise." />
